<br>
Reward vs time vs risk.<br>
<br>
Reward = a Fungi.<br>
<br>
Reward = reasonable exp (not the best, but pretty good).<br>
<br>
Risk = little if you know what your doing. Once the camp is broken it's piss easy.<br>
<br>
Time = Can be a long time now with the drop rate nerf. However, not as long as Raster. ;-)<br>
<br>
A 100K item (well, thats the price of Fungi's on 7th hammer), whilst getting reasonable exp, in a reasonably safe camp.<br>
<br>
And if you have trouble getting casters to go, do what I did way back when. Tell them you will spend half the camp time at Juggs getting spells for them, half at King. (although Juggs is a harder camp than King imo).<br>
<br>
If I needed another Fungi (which I dont.. have 2 now), no way would I spend 100K on one when all it needs is a few peope's help in an exp spot. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showMessageRange?topicID=11803.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=11803.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showNextMessage?topicID=11803.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11803.topic&index=29><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.emailToFriend?topicID=11803.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.threadControl?topicID=11803.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11803.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=11803.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=f